wiring cassandra 4.x's LogbackLoggingSupport uses. Rewrite to DefaultShutdownHook
and JoranConfigurator so the bump to logback 1.5.x in cassandra-4-mvn-dependencies.json
clears CVE-2023-6481/-6378/-12798/-12801/-11226/-1225.

